sequenceDiagram
    participant User as User/CI
    participant K8sAPI as Kubernetes API<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Webhook as KServe Webhook<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Controller as KServe Controller
    participant StorageInit as Storage Initializer<br/>Init Container
    participant S3 as S3/GCS/Azure Storage<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant SharedVol as Shared Volume<br/>emptyDir/PVC
    participant ModelServer as Model Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Gateway as Istio Gateway/Route<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    participant Client as External Client

    rect rgb(240, 248, 255)
        Note over User,Client: Flow 1: InferenceService Creation and Model Serving
        User->>K8sAPI: Create InferenceService CR<br/>Auth: Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate/Mutate Request<br/>mTLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated CR
        K8sAPI->>Controller: Watch Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create Deployment/KnativeService<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>StorageInit: Start Init Container
        StorageInit->>S3: Download Model Artifacts<br/>AWS SigV4/GCP SA Auth
        S3-->>StorageInit: Model Files
        StorageInit->>SharedVol: Write Model to Volume
        SharedVol->>ModelServer: Mount Volume
        ModelServer->>ModelServer: Load Model from Volume
        Client->>Gateway: POST /v1/models/model:infer<br/>Bearer Token/API Key
        Gateway->>ModelServer: Forward Request<br/>mTLS (Istio) or TLS
        ModelServer-->>Gateway: Inference Result
        Gateway-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    rect rgb(255, 250, 240)
        Note over User,Client: Flow 2: InferenceGraph Multi-Model Pipeline
        Client->>Gateway: Inference Request<br/>443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
        Gateway->>Router: Route to InferenceGraph<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Router->>Transformer: Pre-process Request<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Transformer->>Predictor: Forward Transformed Data<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Predictor->>Explainer: Optional Explanation<br/>80/TCP HTTP mTLS
        Explainer-->>Router: Explanation Result<br/>mTLS
        Predictor-->>Router: Prediction Result<br/>mTLS
        Router-->>Gateway: Aggregated Response<br/>mTLS
        Gateway-->>Client: 443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.2+
    end

    rect rgb(240, 255, 240)
        Note over User,Client: Flow 3: LLM Inference Service Deployment
        User->>K8sAPI: Create LLMInferenceService CR<br/>6443/TCP HTTPS Bearer Token
        K8sAPI->>Webhook: Validate Request<br/>9443/TCP HTTPS mTLS
        Webhook-->>K8sAPI: Validated
        K8sAPI->>Controller: LLMInferenceService Event<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        Controller->>K8sAPI: Create LLM Deployment<br/>ServiceAccount Token
        K8sAPI->>StorageInit: Initialize Storage
        StorageInit->>HFHub: Download LLM Model<br/>443/TCP HTTPS HF Token
        HFHub-->>StorageInit: Model Weights
        StorageInit->>SharedVol: Write to Volume
        SharedVol->>LLMServer: Mount Model
        LLMServer->>LLMServer: Load Model on GPU
        Client->>Route: POST /v1/chat/completions<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3 Bearer Token
        Route->>LLMServer: Forward Request<br/>8080/TCP HTTP mTLS + Authorino JWT
        LLMServer-->>Route: LLM Response
        Route-->>Client: JSON Response
    end

    participant Router as InferenceGraph Router
    participant Transformer as Transformer Service
    participant Predictor as Predictor Service
    participant Explainer as Explainer Service
    participant HFHub as HuggingFace Hub<br/>443/TCP HTTPS
    participant LLMServer as vLLM/TGI Server<br/>8080/TCP HTTP
    participant Route as OpenShift Route/VirtualService<br/>443/TCP HTTPS TLS1.3
